sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as kserve-webhook-server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant Controller as kserve-controller-manager<br/>Watches CRDs
    participant KnativeAPI as Knative/Istio APIs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant VirtualService as Istio VirtualService<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant KnativeService as Knative Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>9081/TCP HTTP
    participant Agent as Agent Sidecar<br/>9081/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Eventing as Knative Eventing Broker<br/>80/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Eventing: Flow 1: Model Deployment and Serving

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated InferenceService
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService event
    Controller->>KnativeAPI: Create Knative Service / Istio VirtualService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    KnativeAPI-->>Controller: Resources created

    Note over StorageInit,ModelServer: Pod initialization

    StorageInit->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM / GCP SA / Azure Key
    S3-->>StorageInit: Model files
    StorageInit->>ModelServer: Copy to /mnt/models<br/>Local filesystem

    Note over Client,Eventing: Flow 2: Inference Request (External → Model)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Optional Bearer Token
    Gateway->>VirtualService: Forward request<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)<br/>Istio Peer Authentication
    VirtualService->>KnativeService: Route to service<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)<br/>Istio Authorization Policy
    KnativeService->>Activator: HTTP request<br/>Knative routing
    Activator->>Agent: Inference request<br/>9081/TCP HTTP
    Agent->>ModelServer: Forward to model<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    ModelServer-->>Agent: Prediction result
    Agent->>Eventing: Send request/response logs<br/>80/TCP HTTP (async)
    Agent-->>Activator: Response
    Activator-->>KnativeService: Response
    KnativeService-->>VirtualService: Response
    VirtualService-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
